Ranger Help for: dodge
======================

SYNTAX:      dodge
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     20 + martial level
SKILL TYPE:  attack

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to enter an active dodging stance, granting
a passive evasion buff for a limited duration. While active, the Ranger
has an increased chance to dodge incoming attacks. The SP cost increases
with the Ranger's martial skill level, but so does the effectiveness
of the evasion. The Ranger must be in combat to use this skill.
